article.description: — Jordan Davis had 18 points as Jacksonville topped North Carolina A&T 63-54 on Saturday.
article.headline: Davis leads Jacksonville past NC A&T 63-54
article.linkText: Davis leads Jacksonville past NC A&T 63-54
article.story: JACKSONVILLE, Fla. -- — Jordan Davis had 18 points as Jacksonville topped North Carolina A&T 63-54 on Saturday. Mike Marsh had 12 points and eight rebounds for Jacksonville (2-0). Bryce Workman added 10 points. Tyreese Davis had seven rebounds. David Beatty had 12 points for the Aggies (0-2). Kameron Langley added 12 points and five steals.
